_sText:
This is an improved version of my map de_tehdas (factory). It has multiple improvements, fixes and enhancements to the map. I recommend updating as this version will fix some irritating fade and graphical bugs. There has not been critical bugs to fix.

Some of the changes:

- Fixed fade in props at certain distances
- Removed echo from sounds (no more echo)
- Fixed invalid lighting on some props 
- Fixed T-base ligting to be less bright
- Added minor details and fixes
- Fixed shadows appearing through floor at certain spots
- No more radioactive effect radar
- Added HDR effect
And so on!
